1. Verify where a point is located against a Segment

outputs = LEFT, RIGHT, ON_SEGMENT, ON_LINE (following the same straight line)

**requirements**
language: C++ (any) 
OS: ubuntu 18.04
compiler: g++ v 7.4.0 (lower version is also fine)

**compile with**
```
g++ -I. main.cpp   # will output a.out
```

**launch with**
```
cat data_short.txt | ./a.out 
cat data_long.txt | ./a.out
```
